204
00:11:56,800 --> 00:11:57,320
Shiyi.

205
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:57,720
Hurry.

206
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:58,240
You're a good girl.

207
00:11:58,240 --> 00:11:59,120
