00:16:50,720 --> 00:16:52,000
Marquis Jingyuan,

273
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:53,880
come with us.

274
00:17:00,760 --> 00:17:02,080
I just

275
00:17:03,400 --> 00:17:05,310
lost the game.

